title: Women Seeking Women 123 (Girlfriends Films) (2015)
description:
http://postimg.org/image/5y5n9fabt/


Women Seeking Women is our biggest and most widely known series. With the element of seduction as the backdrop for almost every vignette, the scenes feature anticipation, suspense and drama. As with our other series, costuming includes everything from formal ball gowns to everyday casual wear. Storylines are believable and special attention is paid to the chemistry between performers
